AWS Budgets allows you set custom cost and usage budgets that alerts you when your budget thresholds are exceeded or when you are about to exceed it. 

STEPS IN CREATING AWS BUDGET
Step 1: Search cost explorer in AWS services, click on budget and proceed to click on create a budget.
Step 2: Choose your cost budget then set your budget, name the budget, and add the budget amount.
Step 3: Define your budget threshold, confirm your budget and create. 
